name: Ashish Kesavadas
title: Senior Business Development Specialist & Strategist
summary: Strategic Business Development leader currently pursuing an MBA at the University of Leeds. Proven expert in orchestrating high-impact partnerships, driving revenue growth in SaaS environments, and executing international market expansions. Specialized in optimizing sales cycles, SEO strategies, and operational efficiency to deliver substantial ROI and sustainable business scaling.

experience.description: Spearheading strategic partnerships with major platforms like UNiDays and Amberstudent, driving a 30% increase in inbound leads and over $100K in revenue. Managing full sales cycles across global markets with a 97% retention rate while leading successful localized campaigns in the Chinese market via Xiaohongshu.

Led the launch of the QuillBot Team Plan MVP, generating $300k+ revenue. Orchestrated SEO strategies boosting Domain Rating to 80 and securing #1 rankings. Conducted high-conversion stakeholder demonstrations across North America and EMEA.

Led a team of 20+ associates to streamline workflows, improving operational efficiency by 40%. Spearheaded a Field Investigation project across five metro clusters to mitigate fraud and developed a partner webapp module that reduced turnaround time by 50%.

Managed SaaS renewals generating ₹5M+ in Monthly Recurring Revenue with a 90%+ renewal rate. Developed and optimized qualification workflows, significantly increasing customer retention and process efficiency.

Achieved ₹10M+ in annual sales revenue, exceeding targets by 15% through strategic B2C sales. Managed a pipeline of 500+ prospective customers with a 30% conversion rate through consultative engagement.
